soot.jimple.spark.geom.utils

Class ZArrayNumberer<E extends Numberable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.spark.geom.utils.ZArrayNumberer<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, IterableNumberer<E>, Numberer<E>

    public class ZArrayNumberer<E extends Numberable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IterableNumberer<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Similar to the ArrayNumberer class in soot. But, this class counts the objects from zero. And, we permit the deletion of objects from the array container. And most importantly, we permits the search for a particular object efficiently. Therefore, this class supports efficiently insert, lookup, deletion and traversal queries.
